                            <h3 class="edu-green">Choose your own pay scale.</h3>
                            <hr>
                            <p>Charge what you think you are worth.We provide you with a unique "blank-canvas" style platform for sharing unique skills that returns a fair value.
                            </p>
                        </div><!-- end title -->
                    </div><!--widget -->
                </div><!-- end col -->

            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="row service-list text-center">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 wow fadeIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
